            <title>奧運男飛人「龜波氣功」慶祝，曾開跑前哂《遊戲王》卡、被日媒稱「最快的宅」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/05/noah-lyles/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=noah-lyles</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/05/noah-lyles/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 12:57:43 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[2024 巴黎奧運]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Noah Lyles]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[龍珠]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[龜波氣功]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1254808</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>美國跑步選手 Noah Lyles 在今屆巴黎奧運以 9.784 秒佳績取得男子 100 米比賽冠軍，化身「男飛人」。Noah Lyles 比賽後在全球觀眾的目光下擺出「龜波氣功」慶祝勝利，以經典動作致敬《龍珠》。此舉引起大眾熱議，更被日本媒體稱其為「世上跑得最快的動漫迷」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240805at-8.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254815" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240805at-8-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240805at-8-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240805at-8.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>現年 27 歲的 Noah Lyles 向來熱愛日本文化，之前亦曾在 6 月的奧運選拔賽上，在起跑前向鏡頭炫耀《遊戲王》的「藍眼白龍」及「Exodia 禁忌之一」卡牌，並佩戴受《火影忍者》 啟發的配飾。在總決賽後，日本體育報章《每日體育》更於頭條上稱 Noah Lyles 是「人類最快的禦宅族」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/c726a3b6fceff61719d0.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254813" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/c726a3b6fceff61719d0-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/c726a3b6fceff61719d0-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/c726a3b6fceff61719d0.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>龍珠迷 Noah Lyles 在今年年初龍珠作者鳥山明逝世時，亦有於 X 上發文悼念致敬，稱對失去傳奇人物鳥山明感到非常悲傷，指鳥山明的作品永遠影響他的生活。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">So sad to lose a legend Akira Toriyama<br />Ik his work has forever affected my life. <a href="https://t.co/KyDPRzr8ng">pic.twitter.com/KyDPRzr8ng</a></p><p>&mdash; Noah Lyles, OLY (@LylesNoah) <a href="https://twitter.com/LylesNoah/status/1766190938471211516?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 8, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.citizen.digital/sports/japan-hails-100m-champ-lyles-as-worlds-fastest-anime-fan-n347158">Citizen Digital</a>、<a href="https://nextshark.com/usa-runner-noah-lyles-yu-gi-oh-cards-olympic-trials">Next Shark</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/05/olympics/life-tech/sport-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">巴黎奧運「中國製」無處不在，阿里雲提供直播技術 + 主導官方紀念品市場</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/cheungkalong-ig-spam-by-italian/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">張家朗 IG 被意大利人洗版鬧偷金牌　意大利劍擊聯盟為賽果提抗議</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/summer-olympics-apple-maps-update/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Maps 推出更新，為巴黎奧運揭幕作準備</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/05/noah-lyles/game-channel/">奧運男飛人「龜波氣功」慶祝，曾開跑前哂《遊戲王》卡、被日媒稱「最快的宅」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
